WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.770 align:middle line:90%


00:00:00.770 --> 00:00:03.160 align:middle line:84%
>>Dr. Lorraine Day did
something most people

00:00:03.160 --> 00:00:05.000 align:middle line:90%
haven't had the courage to do.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:07.310 align:middle line:84%
When diagnosed with
cancer, she decided

00:00:07.310 --> 00:00:10.790 align:middle line:84%
to heal herself without the
aid of the medical community.

00:00:10.790 --> 00:00:13.060 align:middle line:84%
What makes this story
particularly interesting

00:00:13.060 --> 00:00:16.950 align:middle line:84%
is that she herself is a highly
respected orthopedic surgeon.

00:00:16.950 --> 00:00:19.910 align:middle line:84%
Instead, after 30
years as an agnostic,

00:00:19.910 --> 00:00:22.790 align:middle line:84%
she turned to belief and an
ancient recipe for health

00:00:22.790 --> 00:00:24.970 align:middle line:84%
from the Old Testament
after she learned

00:00:24.970 --> 00:00:26.170 align:middle line:90%
that the cancer had spread.

00:00:26.170 --> 00:00:35.990 align:middle line:90%


00:00:35.990 --> 00:00:39.950 align:middle line:84%
>>So let's start a little
bit with your own story

00:00:39.950 --> 00:00:42.090 align:middle line:84%
and how you ended up
where you are today.

00:00:42.090 --> 00:00:43.950 align:middle line:84%
And some of it
was pretty trying,

00:00:43.950 --> 00:00:45.076 align:middle line:90%
physically and otherwise.

00:00:45.076 --> 00:00:45.950 align:middle line:90%
>>Well, that's right.

00:00:45.950 --> 00:00:51.100 align:middle line:84%
I developed cancer in 1992
with a very small lump.

00:00:51.100 --> 00:00:54.240 align:middle line:84%
It was about half the size
of an almond or even smaller.

00:00:54.240 --> 00:00:56.565 align:middle line:84%
And it just bothered me
when I put my seat belt on.

00:00:56.565 --> 00:00:57.940 align:middle line:84%
And I didn't think
it was cancer,

00:00:57.940 --> 00:01:00.100 align:middle line:84%
because it was high
up on my chest.

00:01:00.100 --> 00:01:02.977 align:middle line:84%
And the plastic surgeon that
did the biopsy at Loma Linda

00:01:02.977 --> 00:01:05.060 align:middle line:84%
University, he didn't think
it was cancer, either.

00:01:05.060 --> 00:01:07.640 align:middle line:90%
And I had it done under local.

00:01:07.640 --> 00:01:09.690 align:middle line:84%
But then he called
me a few days later

00:01:09.690 --> 00:01:13.190 align:middle line:84%
and said that not only
did I have cancer,

00:01:13.190 --> 00:01:14.920 align:middle line:84%
but there were
not clear margins.

00:01:14.920 --> 00:01:17.760 align:middle line:84%
It had already spread
into my chest wall.

00:01:17.760 --> 00:01:19.260 align:middle line:90%
So I had another biopsy.

00:01:19.260 --> 00:01:23.700 align:middle line:84%
At that time, I actually
thought you can cut cancer out.

00:01:23.700 --> 00:01:28.250 align:middle line:84%
Now I know you cannot cut cancer
out and get rid of it that way,

00:01:28.250 --> 00:01:32.340 align:middle line:84%
because all the factors that
allowed the cancer to develop

00:01:32.340 --> 00:01:35.200 align:middle line:84%
are still present in your
body unless you change the way

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:37.810 align:middle line:84%
you're eating and living and
everything about your life.

00:01:37.810 --> 00:01:41.220 align:middle line:84%
And so I had another
biopsy done down

00:01:41.220 --> 00:01:43.940 align:middle line:90%
at Scripps Hospital in La Jolla.

00:01:43.940 --> 00:01:45.140 align:middle line:90%
It's near San Diego.

00:01:45.140 --> 00:01:49.010 align:middle line:84%
And I let them put me to
sleep to see if they could get

00:01:49.010 --> 00:01:51.270 align:middle line:84%
clear margins, which
they still could not get.

00:01:51.270 --> 00:01:55.260 align:middle line:84%
I told them, you
cannot do a mastectomy,

00:01:55.260 --> 00:01:56.750 align:middle line:90%
which they recommended.

00:01:56.750 --> 00:02:00.890 align:middle line:84%
And I said I was not going
to do chemo or radiation.

00:02:00.890 --> 00:02:03.830 align:middle line:84%
Well, the interesting thing
is both of my surgeons

00:02:03.830 --> 00:02:06.430 align:middle line:90%
were personal friends.

00:02:06.430 --> 00:02:09.270 align:middle line:84%
One was from-- that
I knew in college.

00:02:09.270 --> 00:02:14.070 align:middle line:84%
And the other one was a resident
with me at UC San Francisco.

00:02:14.070 --> 00:02:16.260 align:middle line:84%
And they thought I had
lost my mind, because I

00:02:16.260 --> 00:02:18.750 align:middle line:84%
said I'm not doing chemo,
I'm not doing radiation.

00:02:18.750 --> 00:02:19.920 align:middle line:90%
And they said, why not?

00:02:19.920 --> 00:02:23.150 align:middle line:84%
And I said, well,
chemotherapy is poison.

00:02:23.150 --> 00:02:25.960 align:middle line:84%
And I said, you and
I were both taught

00:02:25.960 --> 00:02:29.647 align:middle line:90%
that chemotherapy causes cancer.

00:02:29.647 --> 00:02:30.980 align:middle line:90%
I said, every doctor knows that.

00:02:30.980 --> 00:02:32.265 align:middle line:90%
The patients don't know that.

00:02:32.265 --> 00:02:34.780 align:middle line:84%
The patients are all
surprised when I say,

00:02:34.780 --> 00:02:36.230 align:middle line:90%
chemotherapy causes cancer.

00:02:36.230 --> 00:02:38.420 align:middle line:84%
And they'd say, my
doctor wouldn't give me

00:02:38.420 --> 00:02:40.880 align:middle line:84%
something that causes cancer
when I already have cancer.

00:02:40.880 --> 00:02:42.570 align:middle line:84%
And I say, yes, they
would, because they

00:02:42.570 --> 00:02:44.330 align:middle line:90%
don't know what else to do.

00:02:44.330 --> 00:02:47.410 align:middle line:84%
But by that time,
I had found out

00:02:47.410 --> 00:02:50.860 align:middle line:84%
that there was another
way to get well.

00:02:50.860 --> 00:02:53.810 align:middle line:84%
And I had found that
out because people

00:02:53.810 --> 00:02:56.720 align:middle line:84%
had written to me,
showing me that there

00:02:56.720 --> 00:02:58.780 align:middle line:84%
was a huge cover-up
in cancer cures.

00:02:58.780 --> 00:03:00.510 align:middle line:90%
And I was quite shocked.

00:03:00.510 --> 00:03:02.570 align:middle line:84%
And I investigated
the information.

00:03:02.570 --> 00:03:05.130 align:middle line:84%
And in fact, I had
had my own radio show

00:03:05.130 --> 00:03:07.110 align:middle line:84%
called "Truth Serum,"
where I was interviewing

00:03:07.110 --> 00:03:10.150 align:middle line:84%
alternative doctors at
the time that I found out

00:03:10.150 --> 00:03:13.160 align:middle line:90%
I myself had cancer.

00:03:13.160 --> 00:03:16.420 align:middle line:84%
I didn't know exactly what
to do at the beginning.

00:03:16.420 --> 00:03:19.020 align:middle line:84%
But I did know that I had to
change my diet to a totally

00:03:19.020 --> 00:03:22.580 align:middle line:84%
vegan diet, because during
the time I had my radio show,

00:03:22.580 --> 00:03:24.960 align:middle line:84%
I had been going around the
country interviewing people

00:03:24.960 --> 00:03:27.660 align:middle line:84%
I had heard had gotten well by
natural methods from cancer.

00:03:27.660 --> 00:03:30.190 align:middle line:84%
This was before I
knew I had cancer.

00:03:30.190 --> 00:03:33.910 align:middle line:84%
And so one thing that
all of them had done

00:03:33.910 --> 00:03:37.500 align:middle line:84%
was change to a totally
vegan vegetarian diet, which

00:03:37.500 --> 00:03:40.530 align:middle line:84%
means no animal products, no
meat, poultry, fish, dairy,

00:03:40.530 --> 00:03:43.940 align:middle line:90%
eggs, anything like that.

00:03:43.940 --> 00:03:47.960 align:middle line:84%
Again, the lump was small,
very small, at first.

00:03:47.960 --> 00:03:49.900 align:middle line:84%
But obviously, it
wasn't all removed,

00:03:49.900 --> 00:03:52.060 align:middle line:84%
because I did not
have clear margins.

00:03:52.060 --> 00:03:55.610 align:middle line:84%
So I changed my diet to
a totally vegan diet.

00:03:55.610 --> 00:03:56.980 align:middle line:90%
That was the right diet.

00:03:56.980 --> 00:04:01.250 align:middle line:84%
But it's not enough to get you
well from any major disease.

00:04:01.250 --> 00:04:03.710 align:middle line:84%
>>Now, did the growth
continue at this point?

00:04:03.710 --> 00:04:04.210 align:middle line:90%
>>No.

00:04:04.210 --> 00:04:07.260 align:middle line:84%
Nothing happened for
about nine months.

00:04:07.260 --> 00:04:11.320 align:middle line:84%
And then the tumor returned
right in the same place.

00:04:11.320 --> 00:04:13.960 align:middle line:84%
And on my website, I
show those pictures.

00:04:13.960 --> 00:04:15.510 align:middle line:90%
>>It was huge.

00:04:15.510 --> 00:04:18.019 align:middle line:84%
>>Well, it only-- about
nine months later,

00:04:18.019 --> 00:04:21.422 align:middle line:84%
it just regrew to
the size of a marble.

00:04:21.422 --> 00:04:21.922 align:middle line:90%
>>Right.

00:04:21.922 --> 00:04:23.180 align:middle line:84%
I was just referring
to the pictures

00:04:23.180 --> 00:04:24.770 align:middle line:84%
on your site of what
ultimately happened.

00:04:24.770 --> 00:04:25.270 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:04:25.270 --> 00:04:27.180 align:middle line:90%
>>Right.

00:04:27.180 --> 00:04:29.060 align:middle line:84%
But I knew that I
was in trouble when

00:04:29.060 --> 00:04:31.860 align:middle line:84%
it returned, because I was doing
everything I knew how to do,

00:04:31.860 --> 00:04:35.800 align:middle line:90%
which was just changing my diet.

00:04:35.800 --> 00:04:37.100 align:middle line:90%
It's the right diet.

00:04:37.100 --> 00:04:40.280 align:middle line:84%
But it's not enough by itself
to get you well from disease.

00:04:40.280 --> 00:04:43.340 align:middle line:84%
So I then started
searching around.

00:04:43.340 --> 00:04:46.490 align:middle line:84%
And I tried over 40 different
types of alternative medicines.

00:04:46.490 --> 00:04:49.990 align:middle line:90%
I tried the macrobiotic diet.

00:04:49.990 --> 00:04:54.250 align:middle line:84%
I tried 714-X, the
Rife generator,

00:04:54.250 --> 00:04:56.640 align:middle line:84%
and many, many other
kinds-- long enough

00:04:56.640 --> 00:04:58.670 align:middle line:90%
to find out if they would work.

00:04:58.670 --> 00:05:00.520 align:middle line:90%
And it didn't change.

00:05:00.520 --> 00:05:02.780 align:middle line:84%
The tumor didn't
go down in size.

00:05:02.780 --> 00:05:05.860 align:middle line:84%
Then, about nine months
after that, suddenly,

00:05:05.860 --> 00:05:08.150 align:middle line:84%
over a three-week
period of time,

00:05:08.150 --> 00:05:10.210 align:middle line:84%
the tumor grew from
the size of a marble

00:05:10.210 --> 00:05:11.880 align:middle line:84%
to the size of a
large grapefruit

00:05:11.880 --> 00:05:14.300 align:middle line:90%
that you see on my website.

00:05:14.300 --> 00:05:17.430 align:middle line:84%
And at first, it wasn't
terribly painful.

00:05:17.430 --> 00:05:19.760 align:middle line:84%
But over the next
few weeks to months,

00:05:19.760 --> 00:05:22.050 align:middle line:84%
it became terribly,
terribly painful.

00:05:22.050 --> 00:05:24.090 align:middle line:84%
And I knew I was in
serious trouble, because I

00:05:24.090 --> 00:05:26.990 align:middle line:90%
didn't know what to do.

00:05:26.990 --> 00:05:29.810 align:middle line:84%
And I'd tried all of
these alternatives.

00:05:29.810 --> 00:05:31.690 align:middle line:90%
I tried over 40.

00:05:31.690 --> 00:05:34.310 align:middle line:90%
And none of them worked.

00:05:34.310 --> 00:05:39.790 align:middle line:84%
So I then-- I had started
studying the Bible.

00:05:39.790 --> 00:05:41.510 align:middle line:84%
And let me say
right off the bat,

00:05:41.510 --> 00:05:43.980 align:middle line:90%
I'm not into organized religion.

00:05:43.980 --> 00:05:47.090 align:middle line:84%
And I believe that
Christianity is not a religion.

00:05:47.090 --> 00:05:50.250 align:middle line:84%
It's a personal relationship
with Jesus Christ.

00:05:50.250 --> 00:05:53.930 align:middle line:84%
And I had been an agnostic for
virtually all of my adult life.

00:05:53.930 --> 00:05:56.100 align:middle line:84%
But at this point,
I knew everything

00:05:56.100 --> 00:05:57.670 align:middle line:90%
every other doctor knew.

00:05:57.670 --> 00:06:03.170 align:middle line:84%
And I knew that regular
medicine could not get me well.

00:06:03.170 --> 00:06:04.640 align:middle line:90%
Again, I refused chemo.

00:06:04.640 --> 00:06:06.480 align:middle line:90%
I refused radiation.

00:06:06.480 --> 00:06:09.690 align:middle line:84%
I wouldn't get involved
with any of those.

00:06:09.690 --> 00:06:12.320 align:middle line:84%
And I knew that a
mastectomy wouldn't help me,

00:06:12.320 --> 00:06:15.280 align:middle line:84%
because I didn't
get breast cancer

00:06:15.280 --> 00:06:17.460 align:middle line:90%
because I had too many breasts.

00:06:17.460 --> 00:06:21.870 align:middle line:84%
Cutting organs off or out
does not solve the problem.

00:06:21.870 --> 00:06:23.776 align:middle line:84%
If you keep on doing
what you've always done,

00:06:23.776 --> 00:06:25.650 align:middle line:84%
you'll keep on being
what you've always been.

00:06:25.650 --> 00:06:26.870 align:middle line:90%
So something had to change.

00:06:26.870 --> 00:06:30.170 align:middle line:84%
But I didn't understand
what I needed to change.

00:06:30.170 --> 00:06:33.210 align:middle line:84%
Now, the human body is
meant to heal itself.

00:06:33.210 --> 00:06:38.060 align:middle line:84%
If you get a cut, it will
heal, unless you have destroyed

00:06:38.060 --> 00:06:41.160 align:middle line:84%
your immune system so
much with the way you live

00:06:41.160 --> 00:06:43.440 align:middle line:84%
or chemotherapy or
anything else like that

00:06:43.440 --> 00:06:46.890 align:middle line:84%
or if you dig it open every
day or if you put dirt in it.

00:06:46.890 --> 00:06:49.480 align:middle line:84%
But you have to do
something traumatic

00:06:49.480 --> 00:06:51.810 align:middle line:84%
to the cut on your hand
to keep it from healing.

00:06:51.810 --> 00:06:54.110 align:middle line:90%
The body is meant to heal.

00:06:54.110 --> 00:06:55.780 align:middle line:84%
I just had to find
out the things

00:06:55.780 --> 00:07:00.100 align:middle line:84%
that I was doing to
my body that caused it

00:07:00.100 --> 00:07:04.520 align:middle line:84%
not to heal or to find out
the situation I was in.

00:07:04.520 --> 00:07:06.690 align:middle line:90%
I gave myself cancer.

00:07:06.690 --> 00:07:08.860 align:middle line:90%
I didn't know I was doing it.

00:07:08.860 --> 00:07:09.960 align:middle line:90%
>>Talk about how that--

00:07:09.960 --> 00:07:10.585 align:middle line:90%
>>That's right.

00:07:10.585 --> 00:07:12.510 align:middle line:90%
I gave myself cancer.

00:07:12.510 --> 00:07:14.600 align:middle line:90%
Everybody gives themself cancer.

00:07:14.600 --> 00:07:16.236 align:middle line:84%
And people don't
like to admit that.

00:07:16.236 --> 00:07:17.610 align:middle line:84%
But it's like
being an alcoholic.

00:07:17.610 --> 00:07:19.370 align:middle line:84%
You can't get well
from alcoholism

00:07:19.370 --> 00:07:23.670 align:middle line:84%
unless you admit publicly
you did this to yourself.

00:07:23.670 --> 00:07:26.780 align:middle line:84%
And people have a very
difficult time doing that.

00:07:26.780 --> 00:07:29.430 align:middle line:84%
And they don't realize that
the very things that they

00:07:29.430 --> 00:07:31.290 align:middle line:84%
do every day are the
things that cause

00:07:31.290 --> 00:07:33.720 align:middle line:84%
cancer and Parkinson's
and all that.

00:07:33.720 --> 00:07:36.540 align:middle line:84%
Now, disease is a
spiritual problem.

00:07:36.540 --> 00:07:39.450 align:middle line:84%
It starts in your heart,
because you want to eat and live

00:07:39.450 --> 00:07:41.840 align:middle line:84%
the way you want to eat and
live rather than the way God

00:07:41.840 --> 00:07:44.770 align:middle line:90%
has designed us to eat and live.

00:07:44.770 --> 00:07:46.280 align:middle line:90%
I had to learn that.

00:07:46.280 --> 00:07:47.970 align:middle line:84%
And I started
studying the Bible.

00:07:47.970 --> 00:07:50.280 align:middle line:90%
I was not healed miraculously.

00:07:50.280 --> 00:07:52.860 align:middle line:84%
I was healed the way
anybody else can be healed.

00:07:52.860 --> 00:07:58.110 align:middle line:84%
It was a long, hard struggle
and a very regimented plan.

00:07:58.110 --> 00:08:00.650 align:middle line:84%
And it took 18 months
for me to get well.

00:08:00.650 --> 00:08:03.300 align:middle line:84%
For two years, I was getting
worse and worse and worse.

00:08:03.300 --> 00:08:05.920 align:middle line:84%
And people say, well, how
did you follow your progress?

00:08:05.920 --> 00:08:07.680 align:middle line:84%
Well, I followed my
progress by getting

00:08:07.680 --> 00:08:09.170 align:middle line:90%
worse and worse and worse.

00:08:09.170 --> 00:08:12.720 align:middle line:84%
But I still would not go to
the conventional doctors,

00:08:12.720 --> 00:08:15.050 align:middle line:84%
because I had seen too
many thousands of patients

00:08:15.050 --> 00:08:17.520 align:middle line:84%
die from the treatment
we give them.

00:08:17.520 --> 00:08:19.030 align:middle line:90%
Chemotherapy is poison.

00:08:19.030 --> 00:08:20.280 align:middle line:90%
It causes cancer.

00:08:20.280 --> 00:08:22.010 align:middle line:90%
Every doctor knows that.

00:08:22.010 --> 00:08:26.290 align:middle line:84%
Radiation-- doctors will tell
you, don't get too many x-rays.

00:08:26.290 --> 00:08:27.960 align:middle line:90%
X-rays cause cancer.

00:08:27.960 --> 00:08:29.440 align:middle line:84%
But when you have
cancer, then they

00:08:29.440 --> 00:08:31.840 align:middle line:84%
say, we have to give
you huge doses of what

00:08:31.840 --> 00:08:34.679 align:middle line:84%
we told you to avoid,
because it causes cancer.

00:08:34.679 --> 00:08:39.090 align:middle line:84%
Well, it's because doctors
don't know how to treat cancer.

00:08:39.090 --> 00:08:42.480 align:middle line:84%
We're never taught, because
the pharmaceutical industries

00:08:42.480 --> 00:08:44.890 align:middle line:84%
control much of what is
taught in medical school,

00:08:44.890 --> 00:08:48.000 align:middle line:84%
because they give the majority
of funding for research.

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:50.870 align:middle line:84%
And they only teach
surgery and drugs.

00:08:50.870 --> 00:08:53.940 align:middle line:84%
>>And we're going to talk about
that whole cancer industry

00:08:53.940 --> 00:08:54.780 align:middle line:90%
also in a minute.

00:08:54.780 --> 00:08:55.350 align:middle line:90%
>>Right.

00:08:55.350 --> 00:08:58.120 align:middle line:84%
>>So continuing your story,
you got worse for two years.

00:08:58.120 --> 00:09:00.150 align:middle line:84%
>>So I got worse for
two years until I

00:09:00.150 --> 00:09:01.600 align:middle line:90%
was bedridden for six months.

00:09:01.600 --> 00:09:05.070 align:middle line:84%
At one point, I was not expected
to live through the night.

00:09:05.070 --> 00:09:07.647 align:middle line:84%
And my husband at
the time said, I've

00:09:07.647 --> 00:09:08.980 align:middle line:90%
got to take you to the hospital.

00:09:08.980 --> 00:09:12.120 align:middle line:84%
I said, I'm not going, because
I knew that, if I went,

00:09:12.120 --> 00:09:13.180 align:middle line:90%
they would give me drugs.

00:09:13.180 --> 00:09:16.690 align:middle line:84%
And I had so little life
left in me that I would die.

00:09:16.690 --> 00:09:20.060 align:middle line:90%
So I did pray to the Lord.

00:09:20.060 --> 00:09:22.780 align:middle line:84%
And I said, this is
not working so well.

00:09:22.780 --> 00:09:24.400 align:middle line:90%
I don't know how to do this.

00:09:24.400 --> 00:09:28.100 align:middle line:84%
And God has promised
in Psalms 103:3

00:09:28.100 --> 00:09:30.000 align:middle line:90%
that he heals all our diseases.

00:09:30.000 --> 00:09:32.330 align:middle line:84%
But he does tell us
how he does this.

00:09:32.330 --> 00:09:36.790 align:middle line:84%
In Deuteronomy, Chapter 7,
versus 11 to 15, he said,

00:09:36.790 --> 00:09:40.750 align:middle line:84%
"If you obey my laws"-- that
includes his health laws--

