temperance, fresh air,

00:19:51.400 --> 00:19:54.240 align:middle line:84%
proper rest at the proper
time of night, trust in God.

00:19:54.240 --> 00:19:58.021 align:middle line:84%
I realized that there was--
we don't have within us--

00:19:58.021 --> 00:19:59.770 align:middle line:84%
and I know there are
others who disagree--

00:19:59.770 --> 00:20:02.940 align:middle line:84%
