an external standard,

00:20:09.990 --> 00:20:12.770 align:middle line:84%
and if they do not trust
in God, eventually we

00:20:12.770 --> 00:20:15.830 align:middle line:84%
will run into things in
life that are too big for us

00:20:15.830 --> 00:20:17.680 align:middle line:90%
and that we will go down.

00:20:17.680 --> 00:20:19.740 align:middle line:84%
And so I started
studying the Bible,

00:20:19.740 --> 00:20:25.530 align:middle line:84%
