couldn't help anybody else.

00:20:54.540 --> 00:20:56.800 align:middle line:84%
But I could pray for others
and quit praying just

00:20:56.800 --> 00:21:00.600 align:middle line:84%
for my own self to get well
and pray for other people.

00:21:00.600 --> 00:21:02.680 align:middle line:84%
And so when you get
outside of yourself

00:21:02.680 --> 00:21:06.030 align:middle line:84%
