focusing only on you,

00:21:06.030 --> 00:21:08.340 align:middle line:84%
that is a necessary
part of getting well,

00:21:08.340 --> 00:21:12.970 align:middle line:84%
because everything
starts in the heart.

00:21:12.970 --> 00:21:16.240 align:middle line:84%
The actions that you take
have to start in your mind

00:21:16.240 --> 00:21:17.440 align:middle line:90%
and in your heart.

00:21:17.440 --> 00:21:19.080 align:middle line:84%
And if you want to
live your own way

00:21:19.080 --> 00:21:21.530 align:middle line:84%
and defy all these
laws of natural health,

00:21:21.530 --> 00:21:23.210 align:middle line:90%
