00:29:02.710 --> 00:29:05.410 align:middle line:84%
And when you have it destroyed
with the chemo and radiation,

00:29:05.410 --> 00:29:07.790 align:middle line:84%
yes, it will destroy
the tumor for a time.

00:29:07.790 --> 00:29:10.070 align:middle line:84%
But it also destroys
your immune system.

00:29:10.070 --> 00:29:13.170 align:middle line:84%
And so then, the tumor
will always come back.

00:29:13.170 --> 00:29:14.750 align:middle line:90%
It will always come back.

00:29:14.750 --> 00:29:18.060 align:middle line:84%
If you have enough immune
system left to fight it,

00:29:18.060 --> 00:29:20.510 align:middle line:84%
you may survive for
some period of time

00:29:20.510 --> 00:29:22.120 align:middle line:90%
or maybe for a long time.

00:29:22.120 --> 00:29:26.760 align:middle line:84%
But most people, or many
people, their immune systems

00:29:26.760 --> 00:29:28.300 align:middle line:84%
are so destroyed
by the treatment

00:29:28.300 --> 00:29:30.170 align:middle line:84%
that, when the tumor
comes back, they

00:29:30.170 --> 00:29:31.820 align:middle line:84%
have nothing left
to fight it with.

00:29:31.820 --> 00:29:34.590 align:middle line:84%
Or they give them more
chemo and more radiation.

00:29:34.590 --> 00:29:36.140 align:middle line:90%
And then that kills them.

00:29:36.140 --> 00:29:39.280 align:middle line:84%
I've watched that happen
to so many people,

00:29:39.280 --> 00:29:42.790 align:middle line:84%
including friends of mine who
were too afraid to do what

00:29:42.790 --> 00:29:47.630 align:middle line:84%
I did, because they wanted
to believe the white coats.

00:29:47.630 --> 00:29:49.070 align:middle line:90%
>>And you are a white coat.

00:29:49.070 --> 00:29:50.460 align:middle line:90%
>>I am a white coat.

00:29:50.460 --> 00:29:54.090 align:middle line:84%
And I know that white coats
don't know how to do this.

00:29:54.090 --> 00:29:55.660 align:middle line:90%
They say they do.

00:29:55.660 --> 00:29:59.240 align:middle line:84%
But that's because
we're taught that.

00:29:59.240 --> 00:30:03.870 align:middle line:84%
Doctors fear cancer
more than non-doctors,

00:30:03.870 --> 00:30:08.100 align:middle line:84%
because the lay person
believes that they

00:30:08.100 --> 00:30:10.870 align:middle line:84%
can go to their doctor, and
their doctor can fix it.

00:30:10.870 --> 00:30:13.460 align:middle line:84%
The doctor knows
they can't fix it.

00:30:13.460 --> 00:30:16.940 align:middle line:84%
And doctors talk among
themselves about,

00:30:16.940 --> 00:30:18.610 align:middle line:84%
are we going to kill
the patient first,

00:30:18.610 --> 00:30:20.130 align:middle line:84%
or are we going
to kill the tumor?

00:30:20.130 --> 00:30:23.760 align:middle line:84%
But you see, you can't
just really kill a tumor.

00:30:23.760 --> 00:30:26.410 align:middle line:84%
The body, as I said earlier,
is meant to heal itself.

00:30:26.410 --> 00:30:28.890 align:middle line:84%
What we have to do
is stop injuring it.

00:30:28.890 --> 00:30:32.510 align:middle line:84%
And we injure it by the way
we eat, the way we live.

00:30:32.510 --> 00:30:34.080 align:middle line:90%
This is all kind of trauma.

00:30:34.080 --> 00:30:38.190 align:middle line:84%
If you took a hammer and
hit your thumb every day,

00:30:38.190 --> 00:30:39.650 align:middle line:90%
