00:30:39.650 --> 00:30:42.350 align:middle line:84%
And it wouldn't get well if
you kept hitting it every day.

00:30:42.350 --> 00:30:44.780 align:middle line:84%
You've got to stop
doing the things that

00:30:44.780 --> 00:30:47.350 align:middle line:90%
cause the injury to the body.

00:30:47.350 --> 00:30:50.140 align:middle line:84%
And the problem is that
most people don't know.

00:30:50.140 --> 00:30:52.230 align:middle line:84%
And certainly, the
doctors don't know.

00:30:52.230 --> 00:30:54.580 align:middle line:90%
