natural immune system to reject

00:38:03.870 --> 00:38:04.860 align:middle line:90%
that organ.

00:38:04.860 --> 00:38:06.190 align:middle line:90%
So it's a very dangerous thing.

00:38:06.190 --> 00:38:10.120 align:middle line:84%
And I would encourage people,
